=======
LEGEND
=======

. = Background
# = Wall
P = Player
B = Body
@ = Apple
$ = Pear
% = Plum
& = Strawberry
? = Orange
w = Watermelon
c = Cupcake
" = Sausage
; = Pie
l = Lolipop
: = Salami
h = Cheese
' = Pickle
i = IceCream
{ = Cake
, = Leaf
* = Token
m = Move1
o = Move2
! = Move3
e = Move4
s = Move5
1 = LeftCherry
2 = TopPear
g = GrowthPlum
a = UnripeApple and AppleCounter5
u = UnripeBanana and BananaCounter3
r = RipeBanana
RipeningFruit = UnripeApple or UnripeBanana or RipeBanana
Fruit = Apple or Pear or Plum or Strawberry or Orange or Watermelon or Cupcake or Sausage or Pie or Lolipop or Salami or Cheese or Pickle or IceCream or Cake or Leaf or RipeBanana
SpecialFruit = LeftCherry or TopPear
Segment = WidthSegment or WidthBody

=======
SOUNDS
=======

================
COLLISIONLAYERS
================

Background
Body, WidthBody, Wall, Fruit, SpecialFruit, GrowthPlum, RipeningFruit, Mark, WidthMark, Token, Move1, Move2, Move3, Move4, Move5
Player, WidthSegment
WidthLevel, Width2
AppleCounter5, AppleCounter4, AppleCounter3, AppleCounter2, AppleCounter1, BananaCounter3, BananaCounter2, BananaCounter1
CanEat
TurnMarker
MoveCounter

======
RULES
======

[ WidthSegment ] -> [ WidthMark ]
[ MoveCounter ] -> [ ]
[ Player ] -> [ Player Mark MoveCounter ]

RIGHT [ > Player | LeftCherry ] -> [ > Player | CanEat LeftCherry ]
DOWN [ > Player | TopPear ] -> [ > Player | CanEat TopPear ]

late [ Player GrowthPlum ] -> [ Player Width2 ]

late [ Width2 ] [ Player | WidthBody ] -> [ Width2 ] [ Player | ]
late [ Width2 ] [ | Player ] [ Player | WidthBody ] -> [ Width2 ] [ | Player ] [ Player | ]
late [ Width2 ] [ Player | Mark ] -> [ Width2 ] [ Player | ]
late [ Width2 ] [ | Player ] [ Player | Mark ] -> [ Width2 ] [ | Player ] [ Player | ]

late [ Width2 ] [ | Player ] -> [ Width2 ] [ WidthSegment | Player ]
late [ Width2 ] [ Player | ] -> [ Width2 ] [ Player | WidthSegment ]

late [ WidthSegment Wall ] -> restart
late [ WidthSegment Body ] -> restart
late [ WidthSegment WidthBody ] -> restart

late [ Player Fruit ] -> [ Player ]
late [ CanEat LeftCherry ] -> [ ]
late [ CanEat TopPear ] -> [ ]

late [ Player LeftCherry ] -> restart
late [ Player TopPear ] -> restart

late [ WidthSegment ] -> [ WidthSegment WidthMark ]

late [ Mark no Player ] -> [ Body ]
late [ WidthMark no WidthSegment ] -> [ WidthBody ]
late [ Player Mark ] -> [ Player ]
late [ WidthSegment WidthMark ] -> [ WidthSegment ]
late [ Player Body ]  -> restart
late [ Player Wall ] -> restart
late [ MoveCounter ] [ Token ] -> [ ] [ ]

late [ MoveCounter no Token ] [ Fruit ] -> restart
late [ MoveCounter no Token ] [ RipeningFruit ] -> restart
late [ MoveCounter no Token ] [ SpecialFruit ] -> restart
late [ MoveCounter no Token ] [ GrowthPlum ] -> restart

late [ ] [ UnripeApple ] -> [ ] [ TurnMarker UnripeApple ]
late [ ] [ UnripeBanana ] -> [ ] [ TurnMarker UnripeBanana ]

late [ TurnMarker AppleCounter5 ] -> [ AppleCounter4 ]
late [ TurnMarker AppleCounter4 ] -> [ AppleCounter3 ]
late [ TurnMarker AppleCounter3 ] -> [ AppleCounter2 ]
late [ TurnMarker AppleCounter2 ] -> [ AppleCounter1 ]
late [ TurnMarker AppleCounter1 UnripeApple ] -> [ Apple ]

late [ TurnMarker BananaCounter3 ] -> [ BananaCounter2 ]
late [ TurnMarker BananaCounter2 ] -> [ BananaCounter1 ]
late [ TurnMarker BananaCounter1 UnripeBanana ] -> [ RipeBanana ]

late [ TurnMarker ] -> [ ]

late [ Player UnripeBanana ] -> restart
late [ Player UnripeApple ] -> restart
late [ Player RipeBanana ] -> [ Player ]

==============
WINCONDITIONS
==============

No Fruit
No SpecialFruit
No GrowthPlum
No RipeningFruit

=======
LEVELS
=======

MESSAGE In the light of the moon, a little egg lay on a leaf.

MESSAGE One Sunday morning the warm sun came up and - pop! - out of the egg came a tiny and very hungry caterpillar. He started to look for some food.

