MESSAGE That next day was Sunday again. The caterpillar ate through one nice green leaf, and after he felt much better.

MESSAGE Now he wasn't hungry anymore - and he wasn't a little caterpillar anymore. He was a big, fat caterpillar.

MESSAGE He built a small house, called a cocoon, around himself. He stayed inside for more than two weeks. Then he nibbled a hole in the cocoon, pushed his way out and...

MESSAGE He was a beautiful butterfly!

MESSAGE The Very Hungry Caterpillar: HARD MODE

MESSAGE Now that you understand the core mechanics of the game, let's make things a little more challenging...

MESSAGE LEVEL 1: Directional Eating Requirements - Certain fruits may only be eaten from certain directions. Cherry: From the left, Pears: From the top, Strawberries: No requirement

